    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“点兵点将数一数，</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>绿眼幽幽墙上住。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>莫要当作玩笑听，</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>小姑娘要吓哭哭！”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150620/extras/76c6c9bcba41c7bd9526e8332c2dfcb1.poster.avif?t=1763299831\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150620/extras/76c6c9bcba41c7bd9526e8332c2dfcb1.webm?t=1763299831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150620/extras/76c6c9bcba41c7bd9526e8332c2dfcb1.mp4?t=1763299831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你听说过那张被诅咒的绿胶唱片吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可曾体验过被“黑毛毯”在深夜勒住脖子的窒息感？是否险些将“蓝手指”错当成香肠夹进面包？《苏联怪谈：绿瞳》取材自真实苏联都市传说，作为五部曲的开篇之作。你将扮演叛逆的四年级学生达莎，因偷听被诅咒的绿胶唱片而卷入诡异事件。直面神秘而又诡异的绿瞳，你能否带领她逃出生天？亦或让她成为新的都市传说？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150620/extras/50173a1c61fe4dba79a61698d3141af8.poster.avif?t=1763299831\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150620/extras/50173a1c61fe4dba79a61698d3141af8.webm?t=1763299831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150620/extras/50173a1c61fe4dba79a61698d3141af8.mp4?t=1763299831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAME FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 回到1986年“改革时期”的苏联，亲历联盟解体前的动荡五年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 复古又温馨的像素画风，瞬间穿越回80年代。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 活灵活现的角色动画和电影式过场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 三种结局：尸体、懦夫与同志。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 尝尝中奖彩票的滋味！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 奶奶的秘制罗宋汤随时供应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 游戏时长约3-4小时。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 沉浸式体验原汁原味的苏联童年！</p>",
